(38, 'Definition and Usage', '<p>The &lt;table&gt; tag defines an HTML table.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An HTML table consists of the &lt;table&gt; element and one or more&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_tr.asp\">&lt;tr&gt;</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_th.asp\">&lt;th&gt;</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_td.asp\">&lt;td&gt;</a>&nbsp;elements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The &lt;tr&gt; element defines a table row, the &lt;th&gt; element defines a table header, and the &lt;td&gt; element defines a table cell.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A more complex HTML table may also include &lt;caption&gt;, &lt;col&gt;, &lt;colgroup&gt;, &lt;thead&gt;, &lt;tfoot&gt;, and &lt;tbody&gt; elements.</p>\r\n', 2, 'HTML', 'cropped-1-1.png', 'saddam hossan', ''),
